Edit the db/migrate files and add options, limits, defaults to suit.

== Create the user amd session authentication

Edit the Gemfile and add,

# For LDAP authentication
gem 'devise'
gem 'cancan'
#gem 'rolify'

Rolify might be useful but we seem to have managed without it previously just so
long as we're happy to build our own role model and integrate with
the User model.

Follow the instructions described in rails_role_based_access_control.txt for
devise and CanCan.



